entries.journal_entry_description: Help an Ewok Child find his lost Festival of Love cards.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Gather all 7 Festival of Love cards and combine them into a nice bundle before returning them. You will find them throughout Tyrena on Corellia, Kaadara on Naboo, and perhaps even at the Southern Ewok Lake Village on Endor.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Find the Lost Festival of Love Cards
